{
  "stem": "3855.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as we walking in front of them-- obviously to scare us that we shouldn't gang up on them and resist or anything, they hit both of us over the head.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Now, my brother's bowler sort of reduced the impact.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But my cap permitted that chair leg to go right through and split my head open.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was bleeding profusely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We came in front of a door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there was this-- it may sound funny, but there was this huge, convertible, black Mercedes standing there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Otherwise magnificent, if it weren't for the situation at the moment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And one was driving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were sitting in that second seat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the second-- the other one was sitting in the backseat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he-- we were driving down to the police station, the very street that I have walked and sauntered and skipped down to go to both of my schools.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And here it was, 6:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And when they-- when we came to the police station, there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "A lone policeman was manning it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they said to him, let's put these fellows in a cell.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I was bleeding profusely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And this cop-- try to use the term-- looked at me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I said to him in Viennese slang, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Which means like, hey buddy, come along, do me the favor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he said to these people, you can't go in here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We have to first take their names and addresses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And believe it or not, these two big guys listened to him and left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I have the feeling that this man saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Because if he had opened the cell door and let us in there with these two fellows, there's no telling what they would have done to us.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
